To make a new instance, put /home/lego/bin/sun4-51 in your path
and invoke

   cml

then type 

  use "build.sml"

finally type the command 

  make_lego true "your favorite message"

replace true by false if you only want legoML.

For profiling, uncomment all sections relating to profiling, use

   nj-sml -profile

then type 

   use "build.sml";
